<plot>Black and White is a hard hitting drama revolving around two brothers, Lee and Rob. Lee is a 14 year old promising footballer. Rob is a 19 year old drug addict, whose addiction ruined his own football career. Owing money to Joe, a local drug dealer, Rob is selling drugs to repay his debt. Running out of time, Rob's increasingly desperate attempts to raise the money lead to tragedy that engulfs the whole family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?073755</url></doc>
